Apple AppStore

agora is available on the AppStore since January 2012.

Android Market

agora is available on the Android Market for devices with at least Android-2.0. Note that the agora-release.apk is also available from the download area.

Cocoa (Mac desktop)

On a Mac, download and unzip the agora.app.zip, then click on the agora icon (or do : open agora.app, from a terminal). Remember that data files are searched within the directory : 

     ~/Documents/agora
